{"title":"坝上的天空（二首）","authors":["毕东海"],"dates":[{"year":1996,"month":4,"day":23}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"坝上的天空（二首）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毕东海"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"夜里站在坝上原野"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"夜里站在坝上原野"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你会发现"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"白天不可企及的天空"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"原来并不比你高多少"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你就和天空"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"并排站在一起"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"夜空"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"很像片静谧林子"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"树的枝条弯曲下来"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"成弧形垂落到遥远天边"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"此刻"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你就站在这林子里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"拥着你的是"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"漆黑漆黑的叶片"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"晶亮晶亮的果实"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你想走动走动"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"忽然担心会被密密枝杈"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"划破鼻子"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"于是你依然站着"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"无言地被感动着"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只到梦悠悠地"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你的双足扎下根须"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"手臂伸出枝杈"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一颗心幻化成枚果子"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"挂上这神秘苍穹"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"独自仰卧草地望空"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"独自仰卧草地看天空时"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你会突然觉得"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那天空真薄"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"透明如蝉翼"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你甚至不敢"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"随意挥动自己的手"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"生恐不小心"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把天空捅出个眼来"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"漏出那背面的黑夜"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这时周围很静"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"静得只有你的呼吸"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"发出惊心动魄的声音"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一阵小风吹过"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"草儿们纤纤手臂垂动"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"此刻恍然坝上是一只船"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"摇摇晃晃"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"飘飘悠悠"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在远远天边"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"溅起几片洁白云朵"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"忽听百灵"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不远处一缕欢鸣"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你宁静的心"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不由被高高衔起"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"很久很久"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"没有落下"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":12,"page_end":12}